across your path! You are Death!

Last nights after effects:

1 Hellacious Hangover
2 Sore arms
1 Cigarrette left
1 Black eye

Why do I feel the need to stick up for people all the time. Guess someones gotta do it. It was a fun night tho =)

Some people don't deserve the air they fucking breath. It's hard to believe that two weeks ago it was a completely different story. I want to do something about it so bad but find myself stuck in a position of limbo. All I can do is tell Brendan I'm there if he needs me....just wish I could get out to Cali for a bit.
